    "1 3rd and 4th Industrial revolution technologies This volume gathers the peer-reviewed papers presented at the 14th edition of the International Workshop on Service-oriented, Holonic and Multi-agent Manufacturing Systems for the Industry of the Future SOHOMA'24, organized on September 26-27, 2024 by the Technical University of Applied Sciences Augsburg in collaboration with University Politehnica of Bucharest (the CIMR Research Centre in Computer Integrated Manufacturing and Robotics), Polytechnic University Hauts-de-France (the LAMIH Laboratory of Industrial and Human Automation Control, Mechanical Engineering and Computer Science) and Polytechnic Institute of Bragança (the CeDRI Research Centre in Digitalization and Intelligent Robotics)."
